AUDIO: 'I want it to work exactly the way the community needs it to work, driven entirely by your feedback. Termux is completely free, and it will always remain open source. So, here is what I\'m working on next.'

[04:54] [scene:talk]
VISUAL:
AUDIO: 'First, real-time auto complete right in the terminal. Then, pluggable LSP. This will be optional, so if you want the full IDE features, you will be able to download it separately, keeping the core app'

[05:06] [scene:talk]
